data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath, concrete block home in quaint Belleview, Florida.  It is located in the quiet subdivision of Belleview's Sunny Skies just on the South side of Belleview off of US Hwy 27 and only about 10 miles from the Villages, Florida.  The home was built in 2022, has 1520 sqft under air per county records, has a large 2-car garage, and sits on a .24 acre lot.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and soft-close white Shaker-style cabinets and drawers.  You can enjoy your morning beverage in the breakfast nook overlooking the backyard which you can access through the glass French doors just off the Living Room.  the Primary Bedroom features a large en-suite with double sinks, a spacious walk-in glass shower, a separate tub, and a large walk-in closet.  Other home features include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, a spacious inside laundry room, ceiling fans, and a whole home water filtration system.  Also ... NO HOA!!!  Enjoy abundant dining and shopping just minutes away in Belleview, The Villages, or even The Market of Marion Flea and Farmers Market just down the road.
